# Senior Code Review ‚Äî iskrib_v3

A comprehensive review of the full-stack web application: React/Vite frontend + Express/Supabase backend.

---

## Overall Impression

You've built a genuinely impressive product solo. The feature set ‚Äî rich text editor, social feed, stories, discovery engine, notifications, SEO, onboarding ‚Äî is ambitious and functional. Your instincts on separation of concerns (controllers/services/routes) are solid. The SEO pipeline, SSRF protection on share images, and React Query cache management show real engineering maturity.

That said, there are some areas that need attention before this scales further. I've organized everything by priority.

